---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Personal Loan @ 9.98% Interest Rate | TrueCred Loan Expert">

<!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <a href="#">Loans</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <span>Personal Loan</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Personal Loan</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Get instant personal loans with interest rates starting at just 9.98% p.a. Compare offers from 80+ lenders and find the best deal tailored to your needs. Quick approval, minimal documentation, and disbursal in as fast as 2 hours.</p>
      <div class="hero-highlights">
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-indian-rupee-sign"></i>
          <span>Loan Amount: ₹50K - ₹40L</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-calendar-days"></i>
          <span>Tenure: 1-5 Years</span>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-percent"></i>
          <span>Interest: 9.98% onwards</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2>What is a Personal Loan?</h2>
          <p>A personal loan is an unsecured loan that you can avail from banks, NBFCs, and fintech lenders without pledging any collateral or security. It can be used for a wide range of purposes such as medical emergencies, wedding expenses, home renovation, travel, debt consolidation, or any other personal financial need. Personal loans are one of the most popular financial products in India owing to their flexibility, quick disbursal, and minimal documentation requirements.</p>
          <p>At TrueCred Loan Expert, we partner with over 80 leading banks and NBFCs to bring you the best personal loan offers with competitive interest rates starting at just 9.98% p.a. Our platform makes it simple to compare rates, check eligibility, and apply online — all in a few minutes. Whether you need ₹50,000 for an emergency or ₹40 lakhs for a major expense, we have the right solution for you.</p>

          <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">9.98%</span>
              <span class="info-label">Interest Rate (p.a.)</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">₹40 Lakh</span>
              <span class="info-label">Max Loan Amount</span>
            </div>
            <div class="info-box">
              <span class="info-value">5 Years</span>
              <span class="info-label">Max Tenure</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Personal Loan Interest Rates — April 2026</h3>
          <table class="rate-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Bank / NBFC</th>
                <th>Interest Rate (p.a.)</th>
                <th>Processing Fee</th>
                <th>Max Tenure</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>SBI</td>
                <td>11.00% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 1.50%</td>
                <td>6 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>HDFC Bank</td>
                <td>10.50% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.50%</td>
                <td>5 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>ICICI Bank</td>
                <td>10.75% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.25%</td>
                <td>5 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Axis Bank</td>
                <td>10.49% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.00%</td>
                <td>5 Years</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Kotak Mahindra Bank</td>
                <td>10.99% onwards</td>
                <td>Up to 2.50%</td>
                <td>5 Years</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>

          <h3>Eligibility Criteria</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Indian citizen or resident aged between 21 and 60 years</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Minimum monthly income of ₹15,000 for salaried individuals</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> CIBIL score of 700 or above for best interest rates</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Minimum 1 year of work experience (6 months in current job)</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Self-employed professionals with minimum 2 years of business vintage</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Stable source of income with proper documentation</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>How to Apply for a Personal Loan</h3>
          <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <h4>Check Eligibility</h4>
              <p>Enter your basic details like income, employment type, and city to instantly check your eligibility.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
              <h4>Compare Offers</h4>
              <p>Browse and compare personalized loan offers from 80+ lenders based on your profile and credit score.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">3</div>
              <h4>Submit Documents</h4>
              <p>Upload KYC documents, income proof, and bank statements digitally — no branch visits required.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">4</div>
              <h4>Get Disbursed</h4>
              <p>After quick verification and approval, the loan amount is transferred directly to your bank account.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3>Documents Required</h3>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Identity Proof — Aadhaar Card, PAN Card, Passport, or Voter ID</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Address Proof — Aadhaar Card, Utility Bill, Rent Agreement, or Passport</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Income Proof — Latest 3 months salary slips or ITR for self-employed</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Bank Statements — Last 6 months bank account statements</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Employment Proof — Offer letter, appointment letter, or business registration</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i> Passport-size photographs (2 copies)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="content-sidebar">
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-file-signature"></i> Apply for Personal Loan</h3>
            <form class="sidebar-form" onsubmit="return false;">
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="Full Name" required>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="tel" class="form-input" placeholder="Mobile Number" maxlength="10" required>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <select class="form-input" required>
                  <option value="" disabled selected>Loan Amount</option>
                  <option value="50000">₹50,000</option>
                  <option value="100000">₹1,00,000</option>
                  <option value="200000">₹2,00,000</option>
                  <option value="300000">₹3,00,000</option>
                  <option value="500000">₹5,00,000</option>
                  <option value="1000000">₹10,00,000</option>
                  <option value="2000000">₹20,00,000</option>
                  <option value="3000000">₹30,00,000</option>
                  <option value="4000000">₹40,00,000</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="City" required>
              </div>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">
                Apply Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-link"></i> Quick Links</h3>
            <div class="sidebar-links">
              <a href="/pages/business-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Business Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/home-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Home Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/loan-against-property"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Loan Against Property</a>
              <a href="/pages/gold-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Gold Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/education-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Education Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/car-loan"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Car Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/credit-cards"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Credit Cards</a>
              <a href="/pages/credit-score"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Credit Score</a>
              <a href="/pages/calculators"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> EMI Calculator</a>
              <a href="/pages/insurance"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> Insurance</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">Got Questions?</span>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p>Everything you need to know about personal loans, answered.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            What is the minimum CIBIL score required for a personal loan?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Most banks and NBFCs require a minimum CIBIL score of 700 to approve a personal loan at competitive interest rates. However, some lenders on our platform offer personal loans to applicants with a score as low as 550, though the interest rates may be higher. A score of 750 or above significantly improves your chances of getting the lowest rates and faster approval.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            How long does it take to get a personal loan disbursed?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              With TrueCred Loan Expert, personal loan disbursal can happen in as fast as 2 hours for pre-approved customers. For new applicants, the typical turnaround time is 24 to 72 hours after document submission and verification. Digital lenders and NBFCs on our platform often process applications faster compared to traditional banks.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Can I prepay or foreclose my personal loan early?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Yes, most lenders allow part-prepayment or full foreclosure of personal loans after a lock-in period of 6 to 12 months. Foreclosure charges typically range from 2% to 5% of the outstanding principal amount. As per RBI guidelines, some lenders with floating-rate personal loans do not charge any foreclosure fee. Always check the specific terms of your loan agreement.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            What is the maximum personal loan amount I can get?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              The maximum personal loan amount varies by lender and depends on your income, credit score, existing obligations, and employer profile. On our platform, you can get personal loans ranging from ₹50,000 to ₹40,00,000. Salaried individuals working in top MNCs or government organizations may qualify for higher amounts with preferential interest rates.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Will applying for a personal loan affect my CIBIL score?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              When you check your eligibility on TrueCred, we use a soft inquiry that does not impact your CIBIL score. However, once you formally apply with a lender, a hard inquiry is made which may temporarily lower your score by 5-10 points. Applying with multiple lenders in a short span can further reduce your score, so we recommend comparing offers on our platform first and applying with the most suitable lender.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page CTA -->
  <section class="page-content" style="padding-top:0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-cta">
        <div>
          <h3>Ready to Get Your Personal Loan?</h3>
          <p>Compare offers from 80+ lenders and get instant approval with rates starting at 9.98% p.a.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline" style="color:#fff;border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);padding:14px 32px;font-size:0.95rem;">
          Apply Now <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->

</BaseLayout>
